milestones.description: Chumney and Ian Billcliff's 23-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 18 between Dennis and Martin Stead
Ian Billcliff and Joe Harris's 22-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 7 between Martin Stead and Marshall
Ian Billcliff and Fazil Sattaur's 26-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 19 between Marshall and Mauricette
Ashish Bagai and Sanjayan Thuraisingam's 12-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 4 between Mauricette and Patel
Sanjayan Thuraisingam and Codrington's 13-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 6 between Patel and Henry
Davis Joseph and Codrington's 21-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 3 between Patel and Valentine
Codrington has become the top wicket-taker for CAN in ODIs with 5 wickets, going past Valentine's 3
Fazil Sattaur has broken the record for most catches (2) in ODIs for CAN, going past Valentine's 1
Ian Billcliff has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (24) in an innings in ODIs for CAN, going past Glenroy Sealy's 20
Davis Joseph has conceded the most runs in an innings (42) in ODIs for CAN, going past Valentine's record of 28
Fazil Sattaur has broken the record for most catches in an innings (2) in ODIs for CAN, going past Valentine's 1
